parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear view mirror stem can cause the mirror to fall off while driving, obstructing the driver's rear view and potentially leading to accidents or injuries.

increased engine noise
decreased engine performance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the tail light mounting can cause the tail light to fall off, leaving the rear of the vehicle without visible brake or tail lights, which can increase the risk of rear-end collisions and accidents.
symptoms: The tail light is loose or hanging by the wire
the tail light is not securely attached to the vehicle
the brake light is not visible
the tail light is missing or detached.
